;[What's New in Firefox] It's now easier and faster to get where you want to go with the latest Firefox.
[Gach Rud Nua i bhFirefox] Tá sé níos éasca ná riamh teacht ar an eolas atá uait leis an leagan is déanaí de Firefox.


;With the redesigned Home page you can now easily access and navigate to your most commonly used menu options.
Leis an dearadh nua ar an Leathanach Baile, beidh tú in ann teacht ar na roghanna a úsáideann tú is minice.


;Like downloads, bookmarks, history, add-ons, sync and settings.
Mar shampla íosluchtuithe, leabharmharcanna, stair, breiseáin, sioncrónú, agus socruithe.


;[New Tab Page] We've also added improvements to your New Tab page.
[Leathanach Cluaisín Nua] D'fheabhsaigh muid an leathanach a thaispeántar le Cluaisín nua.


;With the New Tab page, you can now easily navigate to your most recent and frequently visited sites in one click.
Leis an leathanach Cluaisín Nua, is féidir cuairt a dhéanamh ar na suímh is ansa leat le clic amháin.


;To start using the New Tab page, create a new tab by clicking the '+' at the top of your browser.
Chun an leathanach Cluaisín Nua a úsáid, cruthaigh cluaisín nua trí '+' a chliceáil ag barr do bhrabhsálaí.


;The New Tab page will now display thumbnails of your most recently and frequently visited websites from your Awesome Bar history.
Taispeánfar mionphictiúir de na suímh is ansa leat ó do stair bhrabhsála sa leathanach Cluaisín Nua.


;You can customize your New Tab page by dragging the thumbnails around to change the order.
Is féidir leat leagan amach an leathanaigh Cluaisín Nua a athrú trí na mionphictiúir a tharraingt.


;Click on the pushpin to lock the site into place, or the 'X' button to remove a site.
Cliceáil an biorán chun an suíomh a chur faoi ghlas, agus cliceáil an cnaipe 'X' chun suíomh a bhaint de.


;You can also click the 'grid' icon in the top right of the page to go back to the blank new Tab page.
Nó, cliceáil an deilbhín 'greille' ag barr an leathanaigh ar dheis chun filleadh ar an leathanach folamh sean-nóis.


;Get the latest Firefox now and start using these new features today!
Faigh an leagan is déanaí de Firefox anois agus bain tairbhe as na gnéithe nua seo inniu!
